messages.messageBody:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9dME3NwueNE&list=PLRaLUQfpUj7dNrxNBff8rLEkXn9suE3ed

There will be other things between now and July 24.

I won’t bring them all here, but you could subscribe:

https://learnnothingday.blogspot.com

There will be Macedonian chickens, and a magic trick from Jamaica, and some static art of various sorts.

This is how I celebrate Learn Nothing Day—by collecting more weird art about it. I’m going to give Holly another $50 for the logo she did, too, because I’ve used it like crazy. Once in a while she needs a bonus. It’s not in all of the art, but it’s in some of it!
Someone in Spain put it in a swimming pool, with a cat, sort of:
https://learnnothingday.blogspot.com/2017/07/not-my-cat.html

Sandra
